Pseudocode:

```
for each frame:
    for each point i:
        φ_i += dt * ω_i
        if φ_i >= 1:
            φ_i = 0
            flash(i)
            for each neighbor j:
                φ_j += ε
    draw points with brightness based on recent flashes
```

Brightness can be:

* full white at flash
* exponential decay back to baseline

This gives you the “shimmering field” or “sudden global pulse” look.

